    "MissionGiver": "Headhunters",
    "Title": "Plug a traitor",
    "TitleKey": "headhunters_EliminateSpecific_Defector_title_001",
    "Description": "This shit saddens me. Not sure if you've ever crossed paths with ~mission(TargetName) in your dealings with us. Thought they were a real good one. Been with the Headhunters for years, but something must have happened because they went running to CFP for protection. Sold out some of our brothers and sisters along the way.\n\nAll the Judges are furious and wants blood. That's where you come in. Go to ~mission(Location|Address), find ~mission(TargetName|Last), and kill them.\n\nDoesn't have to be anything fancy. Just want the result.\n\nDamn shame.\n\nStows out.",
    "DescriptionKey": "headhunters_EliminateSpecific_Defector_desc_001",
    "DisplayDescription": "This shit saddens me. Not sure if you've ever crossed paths with [TargetName] in your dealings with us. Thought they were a real good one. Been with the Headhunters for years, but something must have happened because they went running to CFP for protection. Sold out some of our brothers and sisters along the way.\n\nAll the Judges are furious and wants blood. That's where you come in. Go to Remote Outpost near [NearbyLocation], find [TargetName|Last], and kill them.\n\nDoesn't have to be anything fancy. Just want the result.\n\nDamn shame.\n\nStows out.",
